    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E92 M3 featuring the iconic S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies to deliver 414 hp with a linear torque curve peaking at 8,300 RPM. Power is managed via a crisp six-speed manual gearbox and a mechanical M-variable differential lock for optimal traction. The chassis remains taut with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and recent preventative maintenance including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service. Minor cosmetic patina consistent with age, but mechanically robust with a clean subframe and refreshed bushings. A purist\u2019s specification for those seeking the pinnacle of atmospheric M-division engineering.",
