      "description": "This meticulously maintained sedan offers a perfect balance of reliability and comfort. The exterior retains a deep gloss, with only minor road peppering on the front bumper and a few faint hairline scratches consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free environment featuring supple leather upholstery with light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster, but no tears or stains. All power features, including the panoramic sunroof, heated seats, and dual-zone climate control, operate flawlessly. Mechanically, the vehicle has been serviced at strict intervals; the engine pulls smoothly, and the transmission shifts are crisp and predictable. It sits on a set of premium all-season tires with plenty of tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. This is a solid, honest vehicle that has been cared for and is ready for its next owner without any immediate maintenance needs.",
